data.description: Welcome to this charming classic Victorian home, a true gem nestled in a tranquil neighborhood,  where timeless elegance meets modern convenience. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an  abundance of natural light that pours in through the large windows, illuminating the warm and  inviting interior. The tall ceilings throughout the main floor create a sense of openness and  grandeur. The living room, adorned with a charming fireplace and hardwood floors, offers a cozy  space for relaxation or entertainment. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel  appliances, ample cabinet space, and large pantry. Outside, the generously sized corner lot  offers plenty of space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply basking in the beauty of  mature trees and manicured landscaping. A detached garage provides convenient parking and  storage options along with an additional bedroom and half bath. Close proximity to the Beltway and 249!
